        <h1>Ellipse</h1>

        <img src="images/Ellipse/Ellipse.png" height="200px" />

        <br /><br />

        <b>Definition.</b>
        <i>A Ellipse is a plane curve that is mirror </i>
        <br /><br />
    
        <hr />
        <h2>Ellipse Properties</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Has it's symmetry mirrored on each side;
            </li>
            <br />
            <li>
                Subsequently, a concave or convex shape is formed depending on the orientation; 
            </li>
            <br />
            <li>
                It's most extreme-bound point is known as the <b>apex</b>;
            </li>
            <br />
        </ul>

        <hr />

